Ahead of the festive season, Maleek Berry has released two singles, “Wait” and “Doing U”. The singles produced by him are done in his signature style. Wait speaks to the emotional side of the singer who portrays himself as a devout lover holding onto his girl suggesting that they could be secret lovers if she wants it. In the second song Doing U, he is in love with Miss Independent and tries to persuade her that he is for real and is the most suitable partner for her. Enjoy! Wait  Doing U 